@LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:7000
@ContentType = application/json

### Health Check - Verify API is running
GET {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### Get Swagger UI documentation
GET {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/swagger
Accept: text/html

### Get all leave requests
GET {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/leaverequests
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### Get leave request by ID
@LeaveRequestId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/leaverequests/{{LeaveRequestId}}
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### Get leave requests by employee ID
@EmployeeId = 12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc
GET {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/leaverequests/employee/{{EmployeeId}}
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### Create a new leave request - Vacation
POST {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/leaverequests
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "employeeId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc",
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "endDate": "2024-01-20",
  "leaveType": 1,
