### Approve a leave request
@ApproveLeaveRequestId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
POST {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/leaverequests/{{ApproveLeaveRequestId}}/approve
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "managerComments": "Approved! Enjoy your vacation. Please ensure handover is completed."
}

### Reject a leave request
@RejectLeaveRequestId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
POST {{LeaveManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/leaverequests/{{RejectLeaveRequestId}}/reject
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "managerComments": "Rejected due to high workload during this period. Please choose alternative dates."
}

